---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Seguros para Empresas | Andes Protección">
    <header class="relative h-[50vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-slate-900">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2000" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40" alt="Edificio Corporativo" />
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">Seguros para Empresas</h1>
            <p class="text-xl max-w-xl mx-auto">Respaldo sólido para tu patrimonio y tus colaboradores.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div data-aos="fade-right">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">Protege el futuro de tu negocio</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Sabemos cuánto cuesta levantar una empresa. Por eso ofrecemos soluciones integrales a medida que cubren desde la infraestructura física hasta la responsabilidad civil y el bienestar de tus equipos.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 text-slate-700 font-medium">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                        </span>
                        Incendio, Sismo y Robo
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                        </span>
                        Responsabilidad Civil Empresarial
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                        </span>
                        Seguros de Flotas y Transporte
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                        </span>
                        Accidentes Personales y S.O.A.P
                    </li>
                </ul>
                
                <a href="https://wa.me/56912345678?text=Hola,%20quisiera%20asesoría%20para%20seguros%20de%20Empresa" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-blue-700 text-lg">
                    Solicitar Asesoría Empresas
                </a>

            </div>
            <div data-aos="fade-left">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl" alt="Reunión de negocios" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>